description: Factor level shows annual nitrogen fertilizer treatment. N1 applied in autmn, followed by N3 in spring. Not applied in fallow years. Strips 17 and 18, alternating each year with factor N0+3, so N applied in autumn in one year and not the next. Autumn N only applied to winter wheat, spring N3 applied to all crops.
frequency: two applications each year, autumn and spring
treatment_form: ammonium nitrate since 1986, as calcium ammonium nitrate 1968-1985

description: Factor level shows annual nitrogen fertilizer treatment. N3 in spring, no N in autumn. Not applied in fallow years. Strips 17 and 18, alternating each year with factor N1+3, so N applied in autumn in one year and not the next.
treatment_form: ammonium nitrate since 1986, as calcium ammonium nitrate 1968-1985
